This file configures the backing services in docker-compose.yml

Copy this to .env at the root of the project.

--- PostgreSQL ---

POSTGRES_USER=admin
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=secret

DB_NAMEs are set in each service's own .env.example

--- Redis ---

REDIS_ADDRESS=redis:6379

--- Kafka ---

This is the address services inside Docker will use

KAFKA_BROKERS=kafka:29092

For services running on your host machine (e.g., Go main.go)

KAFKA_BROKERS_HOST=localhost:9092

--- Auth ---

JWT_SECRET=this-is-a-very-secret-key-for-local-dev-change-it